# {{computing}} One of a number of [[array]]-like [[data structure]]s where the [[index|indices]] are not limited to [[integer]]s. A collection of memory elements in which each element is referenced by the name of the '''associative array''' together with a combination of one or more [[key]]s, one key for each "dimension" of the array.

